        <h2 id="integrations">CRM Integration Performance</h2>

        <p>CallRail integrates with every major HVAC software platform. Here's how the integrations perform in real-world usage:</p>

        <h3>ServiceTitan Integration</h3>

        <p>The ServiceTitan integration pushes call data, recordings, and lead sources directly into customer records. Setup takes about 45 minutes with ServiceTitan's support team.</p>

        <p>Limitation: Call scoring and conversation intelligence data doesn't sync to ServiceTitan automatically. You need to manually review CallRail reports for call quality insights.</p>

        <h3>Housecall Pro Integration</h3>

        <p>Housecall Pro's CallRail integration creates new customers automatically when calls are identified as appointments. Lead source tracking works perfectly.</p>

        <p>The integration helped Sunshine HVAC in Phoenix increase their call-to-booking rate from 34% to 51% by identifying which marketing sources attracted the most qualified leads. Learn more in our <a href="/hvac/pricing/housecall-pro-pricing">Housecall Pro pricing guide</a>.</p>

        <h3>Jobber Integration</h3>

        <p>Jobber's CallRail connection works well for basic lead tracking but lacks advanced features like automatic appointment creation. You'll need to manually convert qualified calls to jobs.</p>

        <p>For a detailed comparison of these platforms, check our <a href="/hvac/crm/jobber-vs-servicetitan">Jobber vs ServiceTitan analysis</a>.</p>

