        <h2 id="verdict">Is CallRail Worth It for Your HVAC Company?</h2>

        <p>CallRail delivers exceptional value for HVAC companies that meet these criteria:</p>

        <ul>
          <li><strong>Monthly marketing spend of $3,000+:</strong> You need significant ad spend to justify the $95-145/month cost</li>
          <li><strong>Multiple marketing channels:</strong> Companies using Google Ads, Facebook, direct mail, and other channels see the clearest ROI</li>
          <li><strong>6+ technicians:</strong> Larger operations benefit most from call coaching and advanced reporting</li>
          <li><strong>Focus on growth:</strong> Companies actively optimizing marketing performance love the detailed attribution</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Skip CallRail if you're a solo contractor with minimal marketing spend or if you only advertise through Google Local Services (which has built-in call tracking).</p>

